poor credit risks complain they were forced to purchase unwanted 
and unnecessary insurance through claydesta national bank of 
midland as a condition of getting the loans 
in addition to the price of the car most buyers said the loans 
financed insurance policies typically ranging from 1000 to 
7000 that would cover payments in case of illness or death 
